data.enText: in, at or to another place

data.chText: 这个问题的答案必须在别处寻找。
data.enText: The answer to the problem must be sought elsewhere.

data.chText: 我们最喜欢的餐馆已关门了，所以我们只好到别处去。
data.enText: Our favourite restaurant was closed, so we had to go elsewhere.

data.chText: 今天其他地方的天气都比较晴朗。
data.enText: Elsewhere, the weather today has been fairly sunny.

data.chText: 这里的价格比其他地方高。
data.enText: Prices are higher here than elsewhere.

value.def: Elsewhere means in other places or to another place.

example.ex: Almost 80 percent of the state's residents were born elsewhere...
example.tran: 该州居民中几乎有80%出生在异地。

example.ex: They were living rather well, in comparison with people elsewhere in the world...
example.tran: 和世界上其他地方的人相比，他们生活得相当好。

example.ex: But if you are not satisfied then go elsewhere...
example.tran: 但是如果你不满意，就换个地方。

example.ex: Until the doctor arrived from elsewhere on the ward, Amy was in charge.
example.tran: 在医生从别处赶到病房前，这里由埃米负责。
